snippet: Gregor Schlierenzauer finished third in the final event of the Four Hills Tour to become the fourth straight Austrian winner of the ski jumping competition.
lead_paragraph: Gregor Schlierenzauer finished third in the final event of the Four Hills Tour to become the fourth straight Austrian winner of the ski jumping competition.
